txt.en: The DÃºnedain cross into Dunland, a land neighboured closely by Isengard. All are summoned to assist in the passing of this perilous land. They must set a path to the south of Enedwaith, and a seasoned traveller like yourself would be a boon, for surely there are friends to be made in Dunland. You should travel there, and earn what trust you can find amongst the Dunlendings.\n\nElrond
